{"tid":537784,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"問題天天都多","createTime":"2018-01-23T04:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T11:42:09.000Z","uid":98056,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a99bc866c21edfe1a2ded3b3df4f6c3a7b6078f0","tid":537784,"uid":98056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"最近呢排極重負能量 成堆車埋黎<br />\n所以想係度叫下春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說我返工識咗個女仔<br />\n咁大家都有keep住wts app<br />\n但係有時我覺得佢好似唔太想覆我 <br />\n或者覆得有啲hea咁 有時我地可能傾緊兩三樣野<br />\n但係佢就淨係覆得一樣 我講幾句 佢覆一句<br />\n之後咁我sense到 咁我就覆兩三隻字俾佢<br />\n俾機會大家落台 俾佢藍剔我啦 <br />\n之後佢又搵話題講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如是者 loop咗成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好煩 究竟點解<br />\n<br />\n唔想傾咪唔好傾囉 藍剔我咪算 點解要撚我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd58095d36910cb7aff7c888882a27abfdd32d2f","tid":537784,"uid":168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"你自己唔好搵人算啦"},{"pid":"3641112b1e4d2baee432b39d6d9b25ce08a98ccd","tid":537784,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"收兵姐 乖乖地比人收 冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9717cfdce34f2881a2aafe6017eaef5ad0aa4e20","tid":537784,"uid":98056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd58095d36910cb7aff7c888882a27abfdd32d2f","tid":537784,"uid":168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"你自己唔好搵人算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"但係因為一直都有傾緊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533c164fc1c845bb3ce6dfc2b5792d0dd40a8803","tid":537784,"uid":98056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3641112b1e4d2baee432b39d6d9b25ce08a98ccd","tid":537784,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl